data.description: Welcome to this charming country home nestled on 9.7 acres of serene landscape. With 2,229 sqft of living space, this 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms home boasts both comfort and functionality. New floors have been installed with fresh paint and the AC and well were both recently serviced. Large carport in the front yard for you to park your RV or boat.     For those with a penchant for DIY projects or hobbies, the large workshop is a dream come true, providing ample space for woodworking, crafting, or any other creative endeavor. The detached garage offers storage space for vehicles and equipment, keeping the property organized and clutter-free.  Both the front and backyards are fenced.  There is a designated chicken yard that adds to the rural charm of the property. Come prepared to live a country life at its finest!
